{
  "page": "Battle on the river Slayne",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle on the river Slayne</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">Coming of the Andals</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\nBanks of the river <a href=\"/index.php/Slayne\" title=\"Slayne\">Slayne</a> near <a href=\"/index.php/Stonehelm\" title=\"Stonehelm\">Stonehelm</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">Durrandon</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Kingdom of the Storm</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a><br />Three <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornish</a> Kings</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Cleoden_I_Durrandon\" title=\"Cleoden I Durrandon\">Cleoden I Durrandon</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/Drox_the_Corpse-Maker\" title=\"Drox the Corpse-Maker\">Drox the Corpse-Maker</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>A <b>battle on the river Slayne</b> was fought during the <a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">coming of the Andals</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>. An unlikely alliance between King <a href=\"/index.php/Cleoden_I_Durrandon\" title=\"Cleoden I Durrandon\">Cleoden I Durrandon</a> and three <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornish</a> kings won a major victory over the <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Drox_the_Corpse-Maker\" title=\"Drox the Corpse-Maker\">Drox the Corpse-Maker</a> on the river <a href=\"/index.php/Slayne\" title=\"Slayne\">Slayne</a> near <a href=\"/index.php/Stonehelm\" title=\"Stonehelm\">Stonehelm</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_on_the_river_Slayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Stormlands: Andals in the Stormlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404193445\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.058 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.224 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 221/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9148/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7470/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 983/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 697/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.150/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.21 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  215.094      1 -total\n 97.00% 